(42, 19, 17, 42, 16, 10, 10, NULL, 'Faithfulness in Small Matters', 'Both passages emphasize the principle that faithfulness in small responsibilities leads to greater rewards. The connection highlights that being ''faithful in that which is least'' is a prerequisite for greater authority.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
